## 7. Public API Contract

### Authentication
- `POST /api/login`
- `GET /api/me`
- `POST /api/logout`

### Catalog
- `GET /api/products`
  - query params: `page`, `q`, `status`, `category_id`, `subcategory_id`
- `GET /api/products/{id}`
- `GET /api/categories`
- `GET /api/subcategories?category_id=...`

### Customers
- `GET /api/customers`
  - query params: `page`, `q`
- `GET /api/customers/{id}`
- `POST /api/customers`

### Orders
- `GET /api/orders`
  - query params: `page`, `q`, `status`, `customer_id`, `start_date`, `end_date`
- `GET /api/orders/{id}`
- `POST /api/orders`
- `PUT /api/orders/{id}` or `PATCH /api/orders/{id}`
- `POST /api/orders/{id}/confirm`
- `DELETE /api/orders/{id}`

